code: // limit tests to types supporting CopyableValue @Parameterized.Parameters(name = "ID type = {0}, Execution mode = {1}") public static Collection<Object[]> executionModes() {     List<Object[]> executionModes = new ArrayList<>().     for (String idType : new String[] { "byte", "short", "char", "integer", "long", "float", "double", "string" }) {         for (TestExecutionMode executionMode : TestExecutionMode.values()) {             executionModes.add(new Object[] { idType, executionMode }).         }     }     return executionModes. }
